such thing as invisible force fields

19:39.745 --> 19:41.906
except in, like, comic book stuff, right?

19:42.014 --> 19:43.414
- Man, I don't know.
- What is that?

19:43.515 --> 19:45.574
My mama, she had the gift, you know?

19:45.684 --> 19:48.653
