21:06.498 --> 21:09.467
You tried out for the football team
last year, right?

21:11.036 --> 21:12.333
Let's go call your Mom.

21:12.437 --> 21:16.339
Oh, no, no, that... No.
That wasn't like a real tryout.

21:16.441 --> 21:19.137
I was researching a book I was writing.

21:19.244 --> 21:20.541
- Oh, yeah?
- Yeah.

21:20.646 --> 21:23.012
Yeah? What's it about?
Sucking at sports?

21:24.516 --> 21:28.145
