- Yeah.

24:13.251 --> 24:14.582
Yeah, a long time.

24:14.686 --> 24:16.586
Well, do we have any classes together?

24:16.688 --> 24:18.246
- Yeah, yeah.
- Really? Which?

24:18.356 --> 24:21.848
History. Language arts. Math. Science.

24:21.960 --> 24:23.222
- Sam.
- Sam. Yeah.

24:23.328 --> 24:26.764
- Sam Wilkicky.
- Witwicky.

24:26.865 --> 24:28.545
God, you know what? I'm so sorry.
I just...

24:28.633 --> 24:30.328
- No, it's cool.
- I just didn't recognize you.

24:30.435 --> 24:32.869
Yeah, well, I mean,
that's understandable.

24:34.072 --> 24:36.870
No, no, no. No. Come on.

24:38.243 --> 24:40.763
Sorry, I'm just working out the kinks.
You know, it's a new car.

24:41.646 --> 24:44.240
<i>When I get that feeling
I want sexual healing.</i>

24:44.349 --> 24:47.079
This radio is, like, you know...
It's an old radio, too, so...

24:47.185 --> 24:48.880
<i>Sexual healing.</i>

24:48.987 --> 24:51.217
Look, this isn't something that I,
you know...

24:51.323 --> 24:54.292
