I'm gonna walk.

26:13.138 --> 26:14.799
Good luck with your car.

26:17.242 --> 26:18.266
All right.

26:18.376 --> 26:20.310
Walking's healthy, right?

26:21.479 --> 26:23.674
Oh, God, no, no, no, no, no, no.

26:24.082 --> 26:26.346
Come on, please.
Please, you gotta work for me now.

26:26.451 --> 26:29.284
Don't let her walk away. Come on,
come on, come on. Please, please.

26:29.521 --> 26:33.855
<i>Baby come back
any kind of fool could see.</i>

26:34.059 --> 26:35.219
Hey!

26:35.660 --> 26:40.256
<i>There was something
in everything about you.</i>

26:41.933 --> 26:44.458
<i>Baby come back
you can blame it all on me.</i>

26:44.569 --> 26:45.900
Hey!

26:48.506 --> 26:50.167
Wait a second!

26:50.342 --> 26:53.800
<i>I was wrong
and I just can't live without you.</i>

26:55.413 --> 26:56.971
There it is.

26:57.616 --> 27:01.450
I had fun.
So, you know, thanks for listening.

27:02.020 --> 27:06.184
- Oh, yeah, yeah.
- You... You think I'm shallow?

27:07.425 --> 27:10.485
I think you're... No, no, no.

27:10.929 --> 27:15.195
I think there's a lot more
than meets the eye with you.

27:17.168 --> 27:18.135
Okay.

27:19.137 --> 27:20.104
Yeah.

27:20.205 --> 27:22.730
All right, I'll see you at school.

27:22.841 --> 27:23.899
All right.

27:29.814 --> 27:31.281
That's stupid.

27:31.616 --> 27:32.640
That was a stupid line.

27:32.751 --> 27:35.549
"There's more than meets
the eye with you." Stupid.

27:37.956 --> 27:39.321
Oh, God.

27:40.759 --> 27:42.317
Oh, my God. I love my car.

27:53.304 --> 27:58.867
Hey, guys, I think the other team
figured it out. Iran.

27:58.977 --> 28:02.640
Come on, man. This is way too smart
for Iranian scientists.

28:02.747 --> 28:06.513
- Think about it.
- What do you think, kid? Chinese?

28:07.052 --> 28:09.253
No way. This is nothing like
what the Chinese are using.

28:12.857 --> 28:14.722
This is Air Force One.
Level of flight, level three-three-zero.

28:14.826 --> 28:16.885
<i>We will hunt down this enemy.
And when we do,</i>

28:16.995 --> 28:19.190
<i>we'll know just what to do with them.</i>

28:19.698 --> 28:21.893
- Thank you.
- You're welcome.

28:38.717 --> 28:40.318
<i>Apparently, there are
very few survivors.</i>

28:40.418 --> 28:41.612
Yes, Mr. President?

28:41.720 --> 28:44.655
Yeah, can you wrangle me up
some Ding Dongs, darling?

28:56.801 --> 29:00.862
I joined the Air Force to bring the man
Ding Dongs. I'll be in storage.

29:26.231 --> 29:27.198
Shoot.

29:41.379 --> 29:42.903
Gross.

30:10.108 --> 30:11.769
Do you hear that?

30:14.746 --> 30:16.304
Are you getting this?

30:17.315 --> 30:18.955
I think they're hacking
the network again.

30:34.165 --> 30:37.293
Oh, my God. This is a direct match
to the signal in Qatar.

30:37.402 --> 30:39.233
- Are you running a diagnostic?
- Should I be?

30:39.337 --> 30:41.328
- Yes, you should.
- So I am.

30:52.450 --> 30:54.748
Someone!
They're hacking into Air Force One!

30:54.853 --> 30:56.377
We need a senior analyst.

30:56.487 --> 30:58.352
- I think they're planting a virus.
- A virus?

30:58.456 --> 31:00.981
- It's streaming right now.
- They are planting a virus

31:01.092 --> 31:04.289
and stealing a whole lot of data
from your system at the same time.

31:04.395 --> 31:05.919
Code Red. We have a breach.

31:06.030 --> 31:08.760
Air Force One, someone on board
has breached the military network.

31:08.867 --> 31:11.631
I'm in the cargo hold. Clear. Clear.

31:16.241 --> 31:17.640
- You got to cut the hard lines.
- What?

31:17.742 --> 31:20.870
- Whatever they want, they are getting it.
- Sir?

31:20.979 --> 31:23.675
Permission to take down
the Defense Network.

31:23.781 --> 31:27.774
- Cut all server hard lines now.
- Cut all server hard lines now.

31:49.440 --> 31:52.204
Someone's tampered
with the POTUS mainframe.

31:52.343 --> 31:53.776
What the...

31:59.250 --> 32:01.650
<i>Shots fired in the underdeck.
Repeat, shots fired.</i>

32:01.753 --> 32:04.586
<i>Crew, prepare for emergency descent.</i>

32:22.674 --> 32:24.665
I want our President in that bunker.

32:24.776 --> 32:28.803
And I don't want to discuss a damn
thing other till that becomes reality.

32:28.913 --> 32:32.007
That's our first priority.
That's our only priority right now.

32:32.116 --> 32:33.356
Air Force One is on the ground.

33:37.315 --> 33:39.977
Oh, God. No, no, no, no, no, no, no!

33:40.818 --> 33:42.376
That's my car!

33:43.821 --> 33:45.152
