33:47.291 --> 33:48.383
No, no, no, no.

33:55.933 --> 33:58.026
Dad, call the cops!

33:59.804 --> 34:02.932
Where you going with my car, buddy?
Where you going?

34:03.041 --> 34:06.772
Hello? 911 emergency!
My car has been stolen!

34:06.878 --> 34:10.335
