35:22.320 --> 35:24.288
I'm sorry. Mojo, I love you.

35:35.967 --> 35:38.094
No! No! No! No!

35:41.639 --> 35:43.004
Oh, my God.

35:43.574 --> 35:46.099
No, you're a good dog!
