38:30.641 --> 38:33.235
Is that what the kids are doing now?
Little bit of Mojo?

38:33.344 --> 38:36.973
- Those are my dog's pain pills.
- You know, a Chihuahua. A little...

38:40.951 --> 38:42.213
What was that?

38:43.888 --> 38:47.051
You eyeballing my piece, 50 Cent?

38:48.225 --> 38:51.683
You wanna go?
Make something happen. Do it.

38:51.796 --> 38:54.993
